WEBVTT

00:00.935 --> 00:03.352
Be prepared Dad, I will change you,...

00:04.299 --> 00:07.355
...change your goals to get you home earlier every day.

00:08.229 --> 00:10.653
Sometimes I'll give you superpowers,...

00:11.444 --> 00:14.887
...but sometimes I'll make you feel like the weakest man in the world.

00:16.412 --> 00:18.900
I'll test your patience to make your heart softer...

00:19.682 --> 00:21.555
...and your limits to make you tougher.

00:22.121 --> 00:26.507
But I promise Dad, it will be the greatest journey of your life.

